    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>    Wrapper for Python&apos;s built-in dict that supports automatic
    Natlink notification of changes.  The object&apos;s keys are used
    as the elements of the Natlink list, while use of the associated
    values is left to the user.
</verbatim> </para>    </detaileddescription>
